---
title: Garlic & Herb Charred Chicken with Oregano Fries, Greek Salad & Zesty Mayo
description: Zesty! Herby! Creamy! This Mediterranean-inspired meal features lemon, garlic and herbs in an easy marinade for tender chicken thigh, while red onion brings colour and sharp flavour to the Greek-style salad.
